fr.sorbonne_u.components.annotations

Annotation Type AddPlugin


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=TYPE)
public @interface AddPlugin
    The annotation AddPlugin put on a component definition class tells BCM that a plug-in instantiated from the given class must be added to the component with the given URI.

    Description

    The BCM component baseline component constructor will automatically create an instance of the given class and add it to the newly created component with the given URI that can be used to access the plug-in code.

    Invariant

     invariant              true

    Created on : 2017-12-14

    Author:
    Jacques Malenfant
